texts.text: A Bee is a neutral flying mob.

The advancement Bee Our Guest
The achievement Bee our guest
Bee Nest, a natural block that is used by bees to produce honey
Beehive, a craftable block that is used by bees to produce honey
The splash The bee’s knees!
The splash Bees, bees, bees, bees!
The update Buzzy Bees

Bee, a mob that attacks any hostile mob, is passive unlike in the base game
Buzzy Nest, an artifact that summons bees
Beenest Armor, a type of armor that has a chance to summon a bee when the player takes damage
Beehive Armor, a unique variant of the beenest armor
Tumblebee, an armor enchantment that has a chance to summon a bee whenever the player rolls
Busy Bee, a melee weapon enchantment that has a chance to summon a bee whenever a mob is killed with that weapon
